headline: Wolfe Research Affirms ‘Outperform’ Rating on Dollar General Corporation (DG) on Improving Fundamentals
summary: Dollar General Corporation (NYSE:DG) is one of the best FMCG stocks to invest in. On September 18, Wolfe Research analyst Spencer Hanus reiterated an ‘Outperform’ rating on the stock and set a $139 price target.
